<div class="text-center m-5">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Simple</h2>
</div>
<div class="m-2">
  <p>
    You can change the border color depending on the one you want, just change
    the 'card-content-color'.
  </p>
  <p class="font-semibold text-lg mt-2">Colors:</p>
